# Ignore everything by default, then re-include only the paths that
# devnet/Dockerfile actually COPYs. Without this, `docker compose build`
# would try to upload the whole ~55k-file repo root (target/, node_modules,
# frontend builds, etc.) as build context.
#
# Keep in sync with devnet/Dockerfile's COPY lines.

*

# Paths the devnet build needs:
!wasmvm-fork/
!wasmvm-fork/**
!devnet/scripts/init-genesis.sh
!devnet/genesis-template.json
!devnet/Dockerfile

# Even within the whitelisted dirs, drop junk:
**/target/
**/node_modules/
**/.git/
**/*.rlib
**/*.o
**/*.a
!wasmvm-fork/**/*.rs
!wasmvm-fork/**/*.toml
!wasmvm-fork/**/*.lock
!wasmvm-fork/**/*.md
!wasmvm-fork/**/*.patch
